oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Aunt Jemima jingles - Tommy Sosebee
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various Aunt Jemima jingles, plugs, and performances by Tommy Sosebee (performer), the Beasley Sisters (performers), and Louis Buck (announcer), listed as shows #6 and #8.
